@NODE Aguide33 "DreamDoor.library/SendMessage"

    NAME
        SendMessage - Send "OLM" to node

    SYNOPSIS
        result = SendMessage(dif, node, message)
        D0                   D0   D1     A0
        
        ULONG *SendMessage(struct *DIFace, ULONG, APTR);

    FUNCTION
        Send "OLM" to node. User will see the menu when he/she comes to
        the main menu.

    INPUTS
        dif - A Pointer to the DIFace returned by InitDoor()
        node - target node
        message - pointer to message string (Max 300!!)

    RESULT
